Google also kind of "partners" with open-source / free software projects (like [[Apache HTTP Server]], [[MoinMoin]], [[WikiMedia]], [[Xen]] and many others) in their [http://code.google.com/soc/ Summer of Code] projects, sponsoring students working on free software projects and free software project organizations for mentoring them. Google uses lots of free software for their operation and so this is a nice way to "give back".
